U

User - Class in model
The User class defines the attributes for persons who are registered in the database who have access to the Family Map server.
User() - Constructor for class model.User
General constructor for a User object.
UserDAO - Class in dao
This class performs database operations for User objects.
UserDAO() - Constructor for class dao.UserDAO
The general constructor for a UserDAO object.
userList - Variable in class requests.LoadRequest
The list of Users to be created.
userName - Variable in class model.AuthToken
The userName for the User object tied to this AuthToken.
userName - Variable in class model.User
A non-empty String containing the unique identifier for a user.
username - Variable in class requests.FillRequest
The username to be created and entered in the database.
username - Variable in class requests.LoginRequest
The username of the person making the request.
userName - Variable in class requests.RegisterRequest
The userName to be registered.
